"title": "5522: servants, working conditions of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5522",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Those who serve are to be treated fairly and with respect. Jesus Christ himself chose to be a servant and lays responsibility of service on those who follow.</p>\n<h2>Servants are to be treated fairly</h2>\n<h3>They are not to be exploited</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:9\">EPH 6:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:39-Lev25:40\">LEV 25:39–25:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:53\">LEV 25:53</a></p>\n<h3>They are to be paid fairly and promptly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:14-Deut24:15\">DEU 24:14–24:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:15\">GEN 29:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:13\">LEV 19:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:29-Num18:31\">NUM 18:29–18:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:6\">1KI 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:1-Job7:2\">JOB 7:1–7:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:13\">JER 22:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:4\">MAT 20:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:8\">MAT 20:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:4\">ROM 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:1\">COL 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:10\">2TH 3:10</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of servants treated unfairly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:4\">JAS 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:7\">GEN 31:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:41\">GEN 31:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:23-Exod2:24\">EXO 2:23–2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:10-Job24:11\">JOB 24:10–24:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">MAL 3:5</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ as a servant</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:28\">MAT 20:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:7\">PHP 2:7</a></p>\n<h2>Believers follow Jesus Christ's example as servants</h2>\n<h3>They are servants of Jesus Christ and his church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:1\">ROM 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:38\">LUK 1:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:5\">1CO 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:15\">1CO 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:12\">EPH 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:23\">COL 1:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:24\">COL 3:24</a></p>\n<h3>They work to please God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:5-Eph6:6\">EPH 6:5–6:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:22-Col3:24\">COL 3:22–3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:9-Titus2:10\">TIT 2:9–2:10</a></p>\n<h2>Christian workers should be paid honourably</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:17-1Tim5:18\">1TI 5:17–5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:7\">LUK 10:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:7-1Cor9:11\">1CO 9:7–9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:6\">GAL 6:6</a></p>\n<h2>God rewards his servants</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:8\">EPH 6:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:10-Job34:11\">JOB 34:10–34:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:16\">PRO 10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:3-Matt6:4\">MAT 6:3–6:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:23\">MAT 25:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:36\">JHN 4:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:8\">2TI 4:8</a></p>\n<h2>Service of sin has its reward</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:18\">PRO 11:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:1\">HOS 9:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:15\">2PE 2:15</a></p>",
